Class NumberDomain<T extends Number & Comparable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DecimalDomain, IntegerDomain, LongDomain

    public abstract class NumberDomain<T extends Number & Comparable<T>>
extends AbstractValueDomain<T>
    Defines a set of numeric values that can be used by a request.
